snippet.title: Knights of Tartarus Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore an open world and battle your way into the magical dimension called Tartarus.Customize your character, solve puzzles, and find treasures, in this retro turn-based rpg available NOW on PC.

Itchio: https://stello-hexis.itch.io/knights-of-tartarus
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/922920/Knights_of_Tartarus/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/StelloHexis
